<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>207</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Zasiama</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka lung a dawn ni hin,
 Lalpa hung lengin ka lung sungah;
 Liengvai chate chawlhna mun nuom na lenna chu,
 Ei hilhin a chanchin,
 Lei lungkhamna meipi nuoi ahin,

[V2]
 Van mun lopi chanchin chu gensen guol ei puoi,
 Van kingkang phaiphuleng;
 Ei muokna dinguh git hun ni chu.

[V3]
 2. Sietlei thavaih um gam ,
 Lungdawngin luonthi nul mah leng le;
 Thihna luigal ka kaih tiengleh, hehpih Lalpan,
 Aw, ei na muok intin,
 Lungdawn luonthi ei nulsak tan a.

[V4]
 3. Aw zie muna leng chun,
 Khenna thu him him a gen ngei puou;
 Khaw thiengtho leh Belam No chu thu leh zailan,
 Angel vam leh seraf-
 Te chawihatna la chu a chawl puoi.

[V5]
 4. Aw zie mun tung ding chun,
 Sietlei gimtheihna hin ei dal hi;
 Ka ngaklah ie, Na gam thiengtho ei thil sakin,
 Zawhna tum bak chawia,
 Salem thak sung fan kal ka ngaklah.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Lung a Dawn Ni Hin</title>
</song>